   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="Hs-30885,102_001"/><date>23/5 903</date>.</dateline></opener><p>Was ich Ihnen heute zu<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>agen verga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s, <salute>lieber Hugo,</salute> ein Frl <rs ref="#pmb20668" type="person"><hi rend="latintype">Maria Luggin</hi></rs> Vorle<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>erin, früher bei der <rs ref="#pmb11216" type="person"><hi rend="latintype">Ebner Eschenbach</hi></rs> glaub ich, jetzt bei der Generalin <rs ref="#pmb36630" type="person"><hi rend="latintype">v. Hueber</hi></rs>, von<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ympathi<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chem We<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en, will im <date>Herb<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t</date> in kleinem Krei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e
                  (<rs ref="#pmb41254" type="place">Saal des wi<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ch. Club</rs><supplied>)</supplied><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><pb facs="Hs-30885,102_002"/>oder<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>on<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t wo, ungedrucktes (oder möglich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t unbekanntes)
               von be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>eren <rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs>ern <hi rend="latintype">resp</hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs ref="#pmb41240" type="place">Oe<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>terreichern</rs> vorle<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en; bat mich, bei Ihnen
               für<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ie zu reden, was ich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr gern thue. Ich geb ihr jedenfalls was we<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> ich was habe; ka<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> ich ihr
               in Ihrem <pb facs="Hs-30885,102_002"/>Namen Hoffnung machen?</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t<lb/>Ihr <signed>A.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
